18:33.290 --> 18:35.090
OH, YEAH.
YEAH.

18:35.090 --> 18:36.750
NO.
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

18:36.750 --> 18:38.150
SH-- YOU SERIOUS?

18:38.150 --> 18:41.050
