DOES IT TAKE, HUH?

18:52.220 --> 18:55.820
YOU ARE GETTING HUMILIATED,
TAKE ALL YOUR MONEY,

18:55.820 --> 18:58.290
GET EMBARRASSED?
WHAT DO YOU THINK HAPPENED?

18:58.290 --> 19:00.150
SHE SNAPPED AND SHE SHOT
HIS ASS AND THE ONE --

19:00.150 --> 19:01.820
ONE GOOD LAWYER
THAT'S IN THIS TOWN

19:01.820 --> 19:06.290
THAT OWES ME ALL THESE FAVORS
WON'T EVEN REP HER.

19:06.290 --> 19:07.720
I CAN'T, MAN.
OH, YEAH.

19:07.720 --> 19:09.590
BUT YOU GOT THE NERVE
TO SEND ME DOWN SOME --

19:09.590 --> 19:11.190
SOME KID
ALMOST MY SON'S AGE?

19:11.190 --> 19:12.350
YEAH, THAT KID'S PROBABLY
THE ONLY PERSON

19:12.350 --> 19:13.490
THAT'LL REPRESENT HER!

19:13.490 --> 19:14.550
NO, NO, NO.
THAT KID WAS SCARED...

19:14.550 --> 19:15.820
AND HE WAS TERRIBLE.

19:18.490 --> 19:20.650
I'M SORRY, MAN.
I CAN'T.

19:20.650 --> 19:23.120
THAT RIGHT THERE.
THAT'S WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT.

19:23.120 --> 19:24.990
THAT'S WHAT MAKES YOU
SUCH A GOOD LAWYER.

19:24.990 --> 19:27.920
YOU SEE, 'CAUSE YOU DON'T
CARE ABOUT NOTHING, DO YOU?

19:27.920 --> 19:29.120
YOU DON'T CARE
ABOUT NOTHING.

19:29.120 --> 19:30.290
YOU DON'T CARE
ABOUT NOBODY.

19:30.290 --> 19:31.420
AW, MAN,
YOU'RE NOT BEING FAIR.

19:31.420 --> 19:32.550
NO, NO, NO.

19:32.550 --> 19:34.220
EH, I GET IT.

19:34.220 --> 19:36.220
NO, YOU DON'T GET IT.
WHAT DON'T I GET?

19:36.220 --> 19:39.150
I JUST TOLD YOU THAT A WOMAN
TRIED TO KILL HERSELF.

19:39.150 --> 19:40.350
HUH?
AND WHAT HAPPENED?

19:40.350 --> 19:41.420
WELL, YOU KNOW WHAT
THAT MEANS TO YOU?

19:41.420 --> 19:42.490
ABSOLUTELY NOTHING.

19:42.490 --> 19:44.420
SO YES, I DO GET IT.
I GET IT.

19:44.420 --> 19:46.220
OH, COME ON, LUSHION.

19:46.220 --> 19:47.620
YOU KNOW WHAT?

19:47.620 --> 19:50.490
HAVE A GOOD NIGHT,
MY FRIEND.

19:50.490 --> 19:52.350
SLEEP WELL.

19:52.350 --> 19:55.950
ENJOY YOUR NIGHT.

19:55.950 --> 19:58.290
YO, LISTEN, HOW IS SHE?

19:58.290 --> 19:59.890
HOW IS SHE?

19:59.890 --> 20:01.620
OH, NOW IT'S IMPORTANT?

20:01.620 --> 20:05.220
WHY?
I MEAN, YOU DON'T CARE.

20:05.220 --> 20:08.690
AS A MATTER OF FACT,
WELCOME TO THE NEIGHBORHOOD.

20:08.690 --> 20:11.290
AND ANOTHER THING, YOU DON'T
HAVE TO SNEAK TO MOVE IN.

20:11.290 --> 20:13.550
I'M NOT GONNA
BOTHER YOU.

20:13.550 --> 20:15.250
I KNOW WHERE YOU STAND.

20:18.020 --> 20:19.620
LUSHION!

20:19.620 --> 20:27.450
♪♪

20:27.450 --> 20:28.990
YOU KNOW, SOME PEOPLE,
SOME PEOPLE --

20:28.990 --> 20:30.050
WHAT?
I JUST --

20:30.050 --> 20:32.790
WHAT?
WHAT IS IT?

20:32.790 --> 20:36.420
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO GET KELLY
A GOOD LAWYER.

20:38.820 --> 20:40.220
I KNOW.

20:40.220 --> 20:41.650
