20:41.650 --> 20:44.020
MM-HMM.
I KNOW.

20:44.020 --> 20:46.220
AND HE WON'T DO IT?

20:46.220 --> 20:49.750
I TOLD HIM THAT SHE TRIED
TO TAKE HER LIFE.

20:49.750 --> 20:51.750
HE DIDN'T EVEN CARE.

20:51.750 --> 20:54.550
WOW.
WOW.

20:54.550 --> 20:55.820
MM-HMM.

20:55.820 --> 20:58.020
THAT'S HORRIBLE.

20:58.020 --> 21:01.590
YEAH.
I KNOW.

21:01.590 --> 21:05.120
LUSHION, I KN--
I KNOW YOU HAVE SOME MONEY.

21:05.120 --> 21:06.920
OH, COME ON, NATALIE.

21:06.920 --> 21:09.220
AND I KNOW
YOU WANT TO HELP HER.

21:09.220 --> 21:10.920
I KNOW HOW YOU ARE.

21:13.890 --> 21:16.020
LOOK, NATALIE, EVERY TIME
YOU START TALKING

21:16.020 --> 21:18.090
ABOUT MY MONEY AND FINANCES,
JUST SAY WHAT YOU WANT TO SAY.

21:18.090 --> 21:21.350
IF YOU WANT TO GIVE HER
SOME MONEY FOR A LAWYER,

21:21.350 --> 21:23.850
I WOULD APPRECIATE IT IF YOU
WOULD TALK TO ME ABOUT IT.

21:27.020 --> 21:29.290
OKAY, I -- L--
I KNOW IT'S NOT MY MONEY,

21:29.290 --> 21:31.650
