BUT WE DO HAVE KIDS,

21:31.650 --> 21:34.450
AND WE HAVE THINGS
THAT THEY NEED.

21:34.450 --> 21:36.420
AND I UNDERSTAND THAT.
ALRIGHT?

21:36.420 --> 21:37.420
ALRIGHT.

21:37.420 --> 21:39.950
SO LET ME
JUST HANDLE THIS.

21:39.950 --> 21:41.320
CAN YOU DO THAT?

21:41.320 --> 21:42.420
WELL, LOOK, I DON'T
MIND YOU HELPING HER.

21:42.420 --> 21:43.950
NO, NO, NO.
I DON'T MIND YOU HELPING HER

21:43.950 --> 21:45.490
AS LONG AS
IT'S NOT GONNA HURT US.

21:45.490 --> 21:48.620
AND I'M ALWAYS THINKING ABOUT
US, SO LET ME HANDLE THIS.

21:48.620 --> 21:49.890
ALRIGHT.

21:49.890 --> 21:51.520
LET'S GO TO BED.

21:51.520 --> 22:00.550
♪♪

