UH, YES, PLEASE.

22:22.690 --> 22:24.290
THANKS.

22:24.290 --> 22:25.750
NO...

22:25.750 --> 22:27.390
THANK YOU.

22:27.390 --> 22:29.420
[ SIGHS ]

22:32.990 --> 22:35.520
I MEAN IT, MARCIE.

22:35.520 --> 22:37.650
YOU'VE BEEN AMAZING TO ME.

22:37.650 --> 22:39.220
AS YOU HAVE BEEN TO ME.

22:42.590 --> 22:45.520
I'M SORRY ABOUT THE BABY.

22:45.520 --> 22:48.690
