22:51.090 --> 22:53.950
IT WILL HAPPEN.

22:53.950 --> 22:56.550
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

22:56.550 --> 22:57.890
IT HASN'T HAPPENED YET.

22:57.890 --> 23:00.820
I MEAN...
I CAN'T DO IT.

23:00.820 --> 23:04.020
