23:04.020 --> 23:07.690
WELL, MAYBE IT'S JUST NOT
MEANT TO BE WITH HIM.

23:07.690 --> 23:10.490
YOU EVER THINK
ABOUT THAT?

23:10.490 --> 23:12.790
ONCE OR TWICE, YEAH.

23:16.220 --> 23:18.320
I MEAN, THAT COULD BE IT.

23:20.820 --> 23:23.220
YEAH, WELL,
I'M DIVORCED NOW.

23:23.220 --> 23:25.690
YEAH,
AND I WILL BE, TOO...

23:25.690 --> 23:27.350
SOON.

23:27.350 --> 23:29.220
