BECAUSE OF THE KIDS,

23:48.490 --> 23:50.550
SO IF SHE HAS
ANY DECENCY WHATSOEVER,

23:50.550 --> 23:52.320
SHE'S GONNA SIGN
THOSE PAPERS TOMORROW

23:52.320 --> 23:55.220
AND LET ME OUT.

23:55.220 --> 23:58.490
YOU KNOW, SHE DOESN'T
HAVE ANY INCOME.

23:58.490 --> 23:59.350
WELL, I'LL SUPPORT HER.

23:59.350 --> 24:01.490
I MEAN, IF SHE SIGNS
THOSE PAPERS.

24:01.490 --> 24:03.820
