THEN...

24:03.820 --> 24:06.290
I MAY HAVE NO CHOICE
BUT...

24:06.290 --> 24:08.290
TO HIRE A LAWYER.

24:08.290 --> 24:10.420
I MEAN,
ONE THAT I CAN AFFORD.

24:10.420 --> 24:13.690
WELL, YOU KNOW, AS --
AS MAD AS I WAS AT HIM --

24:13.690 --> 24:16.820
LARRY --
HE WAS A GOOD LAWYER.

24:16.820 --> 24:19.490
HE GOT RANDAL
TO SIGN THE PAPERS.

24:19.490 --> 24:21.090
HMM.

24:21.090 --> 24:24.150
YEAH, WELL, MAYBE I SHOULD
GIVE HIM A CALL.

24:24.150 --> 24:27.020
OR YOUR BOYFRIEND.

24:27.020 --> 24:29.950
HE'S NOT MY BOYFRIEND.

24:29.950 --> 24:32.220
WELL,
HE CLEARLY WANTS YOU.

24:32.220 --> 24:35.820
A LOT OF GUYS DO.

24:35.820 --> 24:38.150
JUST NOT THE ONE
I WANT.

24:38.150 --> 24:39.750
