24:39.750 --> 24:42.890
I WANT YOU.

24:42.890 --> 24:44.620
DO YOU?

24:44.620 --> 24:46.020
YEAH, I DO.

24:46.020 --> 24:48.350
I WAS JUST THINKING,
UM...

24:48.350 --> 24:51.350
WHEN SHE SIGNS
THESE DIVORCE PAPERS,

24:51.350 --> 24:54.490
I THINK WE SHOULD, UM,
MAYBE WE SHOULD DATE.

