WHAT?

24:59.690 --> 25:00.690
REALLY?

25:00.690 --> 25:03.820
YEAH.

25:03.820 --> 25:06.190
I MEAN, UH, THAT'S
IF YOU WANT TO.

25:09.420 --> 25:10.620
WE SHOULD
TAKE THIS SLOW.

25:10.620 --> 25:13.550
WE'VE BOTH BEEN HURT.

25:13.550 --> 25:16.090
WE CAN TAKE IT SLOW.

25:16.090 --> 25:19.150
