WE HAVE TIME, RIGHT?

25:19.150 --> 25:20.950
YEAH.

25:20.950 --> 25:22.220
YEAH, WE DO.

25:24.750 --> 25:28.750
I MEAN, RANDAL AND ALEX ARE
NOT GONNA LIKE IT, BUT...

25:28.750 --> 25:30.490
TO HELL WITH THEM.

25:30.490 --> 25:31.790
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

