IT COULD BE...

25:42.990 --> 25:45.850
IT COULD BE
ABOUT THE KIDS.

25:45.850 --> 25:46.920
YOU SHOULDN'T ANSWER IT.

25:46.920 --> 25:48.750
OH, LET ME.
LET ME.

25:48.750 --> 25:50.690
COME ON.

25:50.690 --> 25:51.820
YES?

25:51.820 --> 25:54.350
I TRIED CALLING YOU,
UH, SEVERAL TIMES. UM...

25:54.350 --> 25:55.290
Yeah, I know.

25:55.290 --> 25:56.850
Brad, I'm sorry.

25:58.920 --> 26:00.920
