26:00.920 --> 26:03.520
I JUST -- I-I...

26:03.520 --> 26:06.420
PETER HAS A FEVER, UM...

26:06.420 --> 26:07.950
HE HAS A FEVER AND --
AND IF IT'S --

26:07.950 --> 26:09.220
