26:09.220 --> 26:10.950
I-I'M GONNA KEEP HIM HOME
FROM SCHOOL TOMORROW.

26:10.950 --> 26:12.820
SO...

26:12.820 --> 26:16.090
OKAY.

26:16.090 --> 26:17.290
AND, UM...

26:17.290 --> 26:20.150
