26:20.150 --> 26:21.550
A-AND I'M SORRY.

26:21.550 --> 26:24.650
I DON'T CARE, ALEX.

26:24.650 --> 26:27.320
LISTEN, I JUST, UM...

26:27.320 --> 26:31.890
I-I JUST WANTED TO CALL YOU
AND TELL YOU THAT I, UM...

26:31.890 --> 26:34.820
THAT HE'S NOT FEELING WELL.

26:34.820 --> 26:37.150
THAT'S IT?

26:37.150 --> 26:38.820
AND, UH, THEY --
THEY BOTH WANT TO KNOW

26:38.820 --> 26:40.290
WHEN YOU'RE COMING HOME.

26:44.290 --> 26:46.420
WELL,
YOU CAN TELL THEM

26:46.420 --> 26:49.290
THAT I'LL SEE THEM AT SCHOOL,
AND I WILL PICK THEM UP,

26:49.290 --> 26:52.150
AND I WILL DROP THEM OFF.

26:52.150 --> 26:53.690
WILL YOU, UM...

26:53.690 --> 26:55.090
A-ARE YOU GONNA COME IN
AND --

26:55.090 --> 26:56.950
AND HELP THEM
WITH THEIR HOMEWORK?

26:56.950 --> 26:58.690
DON'T YOU DARE
DO THIS, ALEX.

26:58.690 --> 27:01.350
